<subSubSection pageId="41" pageNumber="862" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="41.[113,1089,219,627]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,214,251,275]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">Remark.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="DRAKE C. J. &amp; HARRIS H. M." box="[223,489,251,275]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" pagination="95 - 96" refId="ref52606" refString="DRAKE C. J. &amp; HARRIS H. M. 1942: A new Brachymetra from Venezuela (Hemiptera-Gerridae). Boletin de Entomologia Venezolana 1 (4): 95 - 96." type="journal article" year="1942">DRAKE &amp; HARRIS (1942)</bibRefCitation>
dedicated the newly described species to Dr. Pablo J. Anduze, mentioning the name three times as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1942" box="[611,835,284,307]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anduze">
<emphasis box="[611,835,284,307]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">Brachymetra anduze</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which is therefore the only original spelling. The species epithet, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1942" box="[591,667,316,339]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anduze">
<emphasis box="[591,667,316,339]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">anduze</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, thus represents a noun in apposition, which contradicts the Recommendation 31A of the ICZN (1999) which however does not make the name unavailable. Subsequently, only 
<bibRefCitation author="RUHOFF F. A." box="[618,774,379,403]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" pagination="1 - 81" refId="ref58844" refString="RUHOFF F. A. 1968: Bibliography and index to scientific contributions of Carl J. Drake for the years 1914 - 1967. United States National Museum Bulletin 267: i - viii + 1 - 81." type="journal article" year="1968">RUHOFF (1968)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="ARISTIZABAL H. G." box="[821,1025,379,403]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" refId="ref50457" refString="ARISTIZABAL H. G. 2002: Los Hemipteros de la pelicula superficial del agua en Colombia. Parte 1. Familia Gerridae. Academia Colombiana de Ciencias Exactas, Fisicas y Naturales, Bogota, x + 239 pp." type="book" year="2002">ARISTIZÁBAL (2002)</bibRefCitation>
listed the name as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1942" box="[248,355,412,435]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anduze">
<emphasis box="[248,355,412,435]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">B. anduze</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="HARRIS H. M. &amp; DRAKE C. J." box="[368,629,411,435]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" pagination="211 - 212" refId="ref53837" refString="HARRIS H. M. &amp; DRAKE C. J. 1945: A new Brachymetra from Peru with list of known species (Hemiptera, Gerridae). Proceedings of the Entomological Society of Washington 47: 211 - 212." type="journal article" year="1945">HARRIS &amp; DRAKE (1945)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="DRAKE C. J. &amp; ROZE J. A." box="[641,882,411,435]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" pagination="227 - 230" refId="ref53155" refString="DRAKE C. J. &amp; ROZE J. A. 1954: New Venezuelan Gerridae (Hemiptera). Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington 67: 227 - 230." type="journal article" year="1954">DRAKE &amp; ROZE (1954)</bibRefCitation>
, and 
<bibRefCitation author="DRAKE C. J." box="[940,1089,411,435]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" pagination="128 - 130" refId="ref52076" refString="DRAKE C. J. 1957: New Neotropical Halobatinae (Hemiptera: Gerridae). Bulletin of the Brooklyn Entomological Society 52: 128 - 130." type="journal article" year="1957">DRAKE (1957)</bibRefCitation>
listed the name as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1942" box="[314,439,444,467]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anduzeei">
<emphasis box="[314,439,444,467]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">B. anduzeei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, while 
<bibRefCitation author="MATSUDA R." box="[520,696,443,467]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" pagination="25 - 632" refId="ref56502" refString="MATSUDA R. 1960: Morphology, evolution and a classification of the Gerridae (Hemiptera-Heteroptera). University of Kansas Science Bulletin 41 (2): 25 - 632." type="journal article" year="1960">MATSUDA (1960)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="HECKMAN C. W." box="[749,927,443,467]" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" refId="ref54071" refString="HECKMAN C. W. 2011: Encyclopedia of South American aquatic insects: Hemiptera - Heteroptera. Springer, Dordrecht, Heidelberg, London &amp; New &amp; York, x + 679 pp." type="book" year="2011">HECKMAN (2011)</bibRefCitation>
used the name as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1942" box="[141,253,476,499]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anduzei">
<emphasis box="[141,253,476,499]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">B. anduzei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but neither of them commented on the change of the spelling or mentioned the original spelling at all so their actions cannot be regarded as emendations. As an incorrect transliteration or latinization of the name are not considered inadvertent errors by ICZN (1999: 32.5.1), 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1942" box="[203,425,572,595]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anduze">
<emphasis box="[203,425,572,595]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">Brachymetra anduze</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
must be accepted as the correct original spelling, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1942" box="[964,1089,572,595]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anduzeei">
<emphasis box="[964,1089,572,595]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">B. anduzeei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1942" box="[159,271,604,627]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="41" pageNumber="862" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anduzei">
<emphasis box="[159,271,604,627]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="862">B. anduzei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
being incorrect subsequent spellings.
</paragraph>
